First and foremost, BE ON TIME.  I am NOT going to wait for someone who is still in SK and doesn't have transport already lined up when I've got groups made up.  I'll wait for you to run from the next zone, I won't wait for you to try to find a ride from the middle of nowhere.  If you can manage to get here before we zone in, great.  If you can't, don't expect me to wait for you.  Last night we got off to a slow start due to an initial lack of clerics.  If that hadn't been the case, I think several melee types would not have made it either.<br>
